race.description: Aussie Rocks Tasmanian Gold Cup H Division2
race.comment: TIMES FLYING (2) won by 2 lengths last start when getting around this track 461m in a head turning 25.84. Can measure up again if runs up to latest time. WHISKY BARREL (1) finished fourth last time at this track but could not have been more impressive before that in his dominant 25.87 win at this track over 461m. Has the ability and can find winning form again. TWO GIRLS (8) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 6 lengths fifth (26.24) last time in a Other at this track over 461m. Rates a key player and gets chance to atone. FUEL ON FOUR (4) placed last start as favourite and is in the mix again.
